{"title":"CF616B-Comparing Two Long Integers","uid":"99c261ee9dc0960e9a2c49422beb7ff3","slug":"CF616B","date":"2021-08-12T03:54:25.000Z","updated":"2021-08-12T13:52:52.265Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/CF616B.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>简单模拟题，可以练习一下优化代码的能力。</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h3 id=\"题意概括\"><a href=\"#题意概括\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题意概括\"></a>题意概括</h3><p>给定一个矩阵，选择一个点，使得其在每一行中最小的情况下尽可能地大。</p>\n<h3 id=\"题目分析\"><a href=\"#题目分析\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目分析\"></a>题目分析</h3><p>原题题意是小情侣一起去吃饭，男的想尽量少花钱，女的想尽量多花钱，于是女的要做最优决策，尽可能地让男的多花钱…</p>\n<p>入门模拟题，读入每一行时记录这一行的最小值，并使之与当前取到的所有最小值做比较，保留较大的一个即为答案。</p>\n<h3 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\">#include &lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;\n#define int long long\n#define maxn 105\nusing namespace std;\n\ninline int read() {\n\tregister char c = getchar();\n\tregister int f = 1, _ = 0;\n\twhile (c &gt; '9' || c &lt; '0')\n\t\tf = (c == '-') ? -1 : 1, c = getchar();\n\twhile (c &lt;= '9' &amp;&amp; c &gt;= '0')\n\t\t_ = (_ &lt;&lt; 3) + (_ &lt;&lt; 1) + (c ^ 48), c = getchar();\n\treturn _ * f;\n}\nint n, m;\nint save;\nint ans = 0;\n\nsigned main() {\n\tn = read(), m = read();\n\tfor (register int i = 0; i &lt; n; i++) {\n\t\tsave = 0x3f3f3f3f;\n\t\tfor (register int j = 0; j &lt; m; j++)\n\t\t\tsave = min(save, read());\n\t\tans = max(ans, save);\n\t}\n\tcout &lt;&lt; ans &lt;&lt; endl;\n\treturn 0;\n}</code></pre>\n\n","text":"简单模拟题，可以练习一下优化代码的能力。 题意概括给定一个矩阵，选择一个点，使得其在每一行中最小的情况下尽可能地大。 题目分析原题题意是小情侣一起去吃饭，男的想尽量少花钱，女的想尽量多花钱，于是女的要做最优决策，尽可能地让男的多花钱… 入门模拟题，读入每一行时记录这一行的最小值，...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":832,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"题解","slug":"题解","count":33,"path":"api/categories/题解.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"CodeForces","slug":"CodeForces","count":13,"path":"api/tags/CodeForces.json"},{"name":"恢复OI实力","slug":"恢复OI实力","count":2